Description_lang: Inflicts Unholy damage to an enemy and imbues the caster with the power of the Twisting Nether for $42006d.If the target is afflicted with Flame Buffet, the target will take the additional damage. If the target is frozen, the damage from Chaos Strike will be tripled.If the target is afflicted with Siphon Life, the target will be weakened, taking additional damage.WARNING! Using this ability will consume 2 Charged Crystal Focus.
